http://ifttt.com/terms
As a condition to using the Service or in order to create certain statements through the Service, you may be required to supply IFTTT with certain registration information, including registration information for mobile phones, other mobile devices, or third party sites or services you access through IFTTT. You shall provide IFTTT with your own accurate, complete, and updated registration information. 

Although it claims you need to use complete accurate information for registration the form only asks for username, email and password[1]. I'm not sure this is future-proof since the form may change without changing the ToU and then the real name would be required.

[1] http://ifttt.com/join
